Symbol.Script_3D:
!-----------3d--------------------- if show_el < EPS and GLOB_VIEW_TYPE<>2 then end IF gs_detlevel_3D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat, gs_InsMat, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
! Close Coupled End Suct Pump
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- CLOSE COUPLED END SUCTION PUMP --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed ADDx houseThk/2 REVOLVE 5,360,1+2+4+8+16+32, -houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1, 0,1, 801, -houseThk/2+hR,houseR, 1001, houseThk/2-hR,houseR, 1, houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1001
ROTy 90 CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, 0,0,913, houseR,360,4013 DEL 1
ADD ConPosX_2-houseThk/2, ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2 ROTy 90 REVOLVE 2,360,1+2+4+8+16+32, 0, ConWidth_2/2, 2, ABS(ConPosZ_2), ConWidth_2/2, 2 DEL 2 CUTEND
ADDx houseThk/2
FOR i=1 TO 2 CUTPOLYA 4,1,0, 0.20*motorNeckL, motorR/4, 15, 0.20*motorNeckL,-motorR/4, 15, 0.85*motorNeckL,-motorR/3, 15, 0.85*motorNeckL, motorR/3, 15 ROTx 90 NEXT i DEL 2
MULx motorL/(motorL+motorR/8) ! --- Motor REVOLVE 8,360, 1+2+4+8+16+32, 0, 0.7*motorR, 2, motorNeckL, motorR, 2, motorL-motorBackL, motorR, 2, motorL-motorBackL, 1.05*motorR, 2, motorL-mR, 1.05*motorR, 1, motorL, 1.05*motorR-mR, 1001, motorL, motorR/5, 2, motorL+motorR/8, motorR/5, 2 DEL 3
CUTEND CUTEND ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple
ADDx houseThk/2 REVOLVE 5,360,1+2+4+8+16+32, -houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1, 0,1, 801, -houseThk/2+hR,houseR, 1, houseThk/2-hR,houseR, 1, houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1
ROTy 90 CUTPOLYA 2,1,0, 0,0,913, houseR,360,4013 DEL 1
ADD ConPosX_2-houseThk/2, ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2 ROTy 90 REVOLVE 2,360,1+2+4+8+16+32, 0, ConWidth_2/2, 2, ABS(ConPosZ_2), ConWidth_2/2, 2 DEL 2 CUTEND
ADDx houseThk/2
FOR i=1 TO 2 CUTPOLYA 4,1,0, 0.20*motorNeckL, motorR/4, 15, 0.20*motorNeckL,-motorR/4, 15, 0.85*motorNeckL,-motorR/3, 15, 0.85*motorNeckL, motorR/3, 15 ROTx 90 NEXT i DEL 2
! --- Motor REVOLVE 4,360, 1+2+4+8+16+32, 0, 0.7*motorR, 2, motorNeckL, motorR, 2, motorL-mR, motorR, 2, motorL, motorR-mR, 1 DEL 2
CUTEND CUTEND ENDIF DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 13, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData END
Symbol.Script_2D:
!-----------2d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end IF gs_detlevel_2D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, MEP_cline_type, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 houseThk+motorL, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, houseR, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -houseR, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 houseThk, houseR, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 houseThk, -houseR, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- CLOSE COUPLED END SUCTION PUMP --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN DRAWINDEX 10
DRAWINDEX 20
ADD2 houseThk/2,0 POLY2_B 9, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1, 0,1, 801, -houseThk/2+hR,houseR, 1001, houseThk/2-hR,houseR, 1, houseThk/2, houseR-hR, 1001,
houseThk/2, -houseR+hR, 1, houseThk/2-hR,-houseR, 1001, -houseThk/2+hR,-houseR, 1, -houseThk/2, -houseR+hR, 1001 DEL 1
ADD2 houseThk,0 MUL2 motorL/(motorL+motorR/8), 1 POLY2_B 30, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0.7*motorR, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL, 0.76*motorR, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL, 0.71*motorR, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL, 0.89*motorR, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL, 0.955*motorR, 1, motorNeckL, motorR, 1, motorL-motorBackL, motorR, 1, motorL-motorBackL, 1.05*motorR, 1, motorL-mR, 1.05*motorR, 1, motorL, 1.05*motorR-mR, 1001, motorL, motorR/5, 1, motorL+motorR/8, motorR/5, 1,
motorL+motorR/8, -motorR/5, 1, motorL, -motorR/5, 1, motorL, -1.05*motorR+mR, 1, motorL-mR, -1.05*motorR, 1001, motorL-motorBackL, -1.05*motorR, 1, motorL-motorBackL, -motorR, 1, motorNeckL, -motorR, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL, -0.955*motorR, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL, -0.89*motorR, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL, -0.71*motorR, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL, -0.76*motorR, 1, 0, -0.7*motorR, 1, 0, 0.7*motorR, -1,
0.20*motorNeckL, motorR/4, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL,-motorR/4, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL,-motorR/3, 1, 0.85*motorNeckL, motorR/3, 1, 0.20*motorNeckL, motorR/4, -1
LINE2 motorNeckL, motorR, motorNeckL, -motorR LINE2 motorL-motorBackL, 1.05*motorR, motorL-motorBackL, -1.05*motorR LINE2 motorL, motorR/5, motorL, -motorR/5 DEL 2
!! POLY2_B 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, !! ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2, 901, !! ConWidth_2/2,360,4001
ENDIF
ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
DEL TOP ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 3, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData DEL 1
END

PARAMETERS ConPosZ_2=B/2

ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = -1 ConWVecZ = 0

IF ConWidth_1<minCW THEN ConWidth_1=minCW PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=minCW ENDIF IF ConWidth_1>maxCW THEN ConWidth_1=maxCW PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=maxCW ENDIF

ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1, ConConnectorTypeFlange_1 = ConConnectorTypeFlange_1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"

ConWVecX = -1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
